				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$0.03 V_{A}$\end{document} at the open boundary. This time shortens to 900 s if the perturbation is enhanced to 0.1VA\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
